Query the two cities in STATION with the shortest and longest CITY names, as well as their respective lengths (i.e.: 
number of characters in the name). If there is more than one smallest or largest city, choose the one that comes first when ordered 
alphabetically.

SELECT TOP 1 City, LEN(City) AS City_Length 
FROM STATION 
ORDER BY City_Length ASC, City ASC;

SELECT TOP 1 City, LEN(City) AS City_Length 
FROM STATION 
ORDER BY City_Length DESC, City DESC;
